[h2]Conquerors![/h2]
We're happy to share that Europa Universalis IV is taking part in Steam's Real Time Strategy Fest. This means sales up to 90% off the base game and 70% select DLC.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/236850/Europa_Universalis_IV/

[img]{STEAM_CLAN_IMAGE}/4678173/8fc26d2b7a441e56c849e3c5e4f2c66094e3f5f2.jpg[/img]

As with other recent sales, we offer the [b][url=https://store.steampowered.com/sub/1134298/]starter edition[/url] at 80% of[/b]f making it one of the best options for brand new players. 

